vote.title: Authorize a Supplemental Agreement No. 4 to the golf-pro concession contract between the City of Dallas and IAMJ Enterprises, Inc., who manages the Cedar Crest Golf Course, to set forth roles, responsibilities, and compensation as a result of the closure of Cedar Crest Golf Course located at 1800 Southerland Avenue - Not to exceed $440,318.00 - Financing:  Golf Improvement Trust Fund
